The paper deals with a synchronization problem in communication channels, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The problem involves editing of binary files, which is a topic in data structures (cs.DS) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The solution involves interactive communication between nodes, which is a topic in networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
